    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, you'd think this beauty just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014it\u2019s in truly pristine, mint condition! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I've taken such good care of it, and I know the next owner will love it just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
