    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This specimen boasts a flawless high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is exceptional, with documented subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive rod bearing service already completed. Finished in Carbon Black over an immaculate Nappa leather interior, the vehicle retains its factory-correct suspension geometry and forged Style 67 wheels. This is a turn-key collector piece with zero mechanical parasitic loss or cosmetic degradation.",
